name: Crewser
body: Crewser is a project to help some event to organise all crews and members and keep track of the ticket and budget status. The project was designed and implemeted by [Computerwerkstatt](http://www.jaz-rostock.de/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=23&Itemid=11) [JAZ Rostock](http://www.jaz-rostock.de/), if you have any questions [get in contact with us](mailto://cwjaz@lists.absorb.it).
